trans-unit.source: Represents the position of the iterator to the next node in the intersection of two sets of nodes.
trans-unit.target: Representerer posisjonen for iterator til neste-noden i skjæringspunktet mellom to sett med noder.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the current result navigator.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir gjeldende resultatet navigatoren.

trans-unit.source: The Current property gets modified when the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A> method sets the Current property to the next node and returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>; otherwise, the Current property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Den gjeldende egenskapen henter endres når den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A>metoden angir den gjeldende egenskapen til den neste noden, og returnerer <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>; ellers den gjeldende egenskapen forblir uendret.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator to the next node in the union.
trans-unit.target: Plasserer iterator til den neste noden på sammenslåingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if there are no more nodes.
Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if this function initializes the right nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>Hvis denne funksjonen initialiserer høyre nestede iterator.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the next node needs to be fetched from the left-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>Hvis den neste noden, må hentes fra den venstre-nestet iterator.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the next node needs to be fetched from the right-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>Hvis den neste noden, må hentes fra den høyre-nestet iterator.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the iterator's <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.Current%2A> property is set to the next node in the iteration.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>Hvis iterator <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.Current%2A>er satt til den neste noden i gjentakelsen.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>
